Featuring: Panic Station, Red Hot Pokers, The Blues Sisters, Roosevelt , Bella Collins Band, Live Dead ’69, Flares, New Street Groove, The Fugitives, James Oliver Band, Freshly Cut Grass, The Marc Davies Band, Stonehouse, Philo Beddoe Band, The Worried Men, Junior Hacksaw, Sassafras, Son Of Man and Expecting Company.
